Summary: I was photographing the sky because of previous sightings and saw this.
divs: Sighting DetailsInitially I was photographing the moon and a rather large star. after taking this photo, I decided to just take random shots of the sky and this is what I got. i don't know what it is. Nor do I want to guess. So I decided to submit this photo and let others see and decide. It is interesting to say the least.
